{"type":"text","timestamp":1775899591903,"sessionID":"ses_2842524b3ffeJcNSdFHyxaSzDZ","part":{"id":"prt_d7bdd33d4001o0mMQEdmGVJ6sD","messageID":"msg_d7bdcee2a001AbP50KAJyOC37v","sessionID":"ses_2842524b3ffeJcNSdFHyxaSzDZ","type":"text","text":"I've successfully written the proposal.md file for AR-043 (架构设计文档与 API 文档). The proposal includes:\n\n**Key Sections:**\n- **Purpose**: Establish a comprehensive technical documentation system for knowledge sharing, development efficiency, and community growth\n- **Scope**: Architecture docs (overview, modules, data flow, security, observability), API docs (REST, gRPC, CRD, SDK), deployment/operations guides, and tutorials\n- **Impact Analysis**: Covers positive impacts (knowledge management, development efficiency) and negative impacts (resource investment, documentation sync challenges) with mitigation strategies\n- **Alternatives Considered**: Evaluated 5 approaches including code-only docs, external platforms, auto-generation, Wiki systems, and static site generators (selected Docusaurus)\n\n**Design Decisions:**\n- Tool: Docusaurus for modern, version-controlled documentation\n- Organization: Multi-layered structure by audience and topic\n- API Documentation: Hybrid approach combining OpenAPI specs with manual writing\n- Version Management: Support for current, historical, and development versions\n\n**Implementation Plan**: 6 phases over 14 days covering infrastructure, architecture docs, API docs, deployment guides, tutorials, and optimization\n\nThe proposal is located at `/changes/AR-043/proposal.md` and follows the project's documentation standards and proposal structure.","time":{"start":1775899591901,"end":1775899591901}}}
